WEBVTT

00:16:57.583 --> 00:17:00.378
To je krivo. To je neodgovorno.

00:17:00.378 --> 00:17:04.616
I najgore od svega, to je dosadno.

00:17:04.616 --> 00:17:08.535
Neka univerzalizam napravi mjesta pluralizmu.

00:17:08.535 --> 00:17:11.732
Možda nam dolazi zanimljivije doba.

00:17:11.732 --> 00:17:13.945
Jesmo li dovoljno hrabri
da mu zaželimo dobrodošlicu?

00:17:13.945 --> 00:17:15.139
Hvala.

00:17:15.139 --> 00:17:31.158
(Aplauz)